== 旅游和签证 ==
[[File:Visa_requirements_for_Slovenian_citizens.png|thumb]]的{{link-en|斯洛維尼亞護照|Slovenian passport}}之[[斯洛維尼亞人口|斯洛維尼亞公民]]可以[[簽證#签证优惠待遇|免簽證]]的方式入境[[巴西|巴西]]。]]
[[File:Visa_requirements_for_Brazilian_citizens.png|thumb]]的[[巴西人|巴西公民]]可以免签证入境[[斯洛維尼亞|斯洛維尼亞]]。]]
{{see also|歐洲聯盟簽證政策|斯洛維尼亞公民簽證要求}}
{{see also|巴西簽證政策|巴西公民簽證要求}}
歐洲[[申根區|申根區]]給予持[[巴西護照|巴西護照]]的[[巴西人|巴西公民]][[歐洲聯盟簽證政策|申根區免簽證]]待遇，停留日數與申根區合併計算，每6個月期間內總計可在斯洛維尼亞停留90天。<ref name = "Reg 610/2013">Article 1 of Regulation (EU) No 610/2013 of the European Parliament and of the Council of 26 June 2013 amending Regulation (EC) No 562/2006 of the European Parliament and of the Council establishing a Community Code on the rules governing the movement of persons across borders (Schengen Borders Code), the Convention implementing the Schengen Agreement, Council Regulations (EC) No 1683/95 and (EC) No 539/2001 and Regulations (EC) No 767/2008 and (EC) No 810/2009 of the European Parliament and of the Council ([http://eur-lex.europa.eu/LexUriServ/LexUriServ.do?uri=OJ:L:2013:182:0001:0018:EN:PDF OJ L 182, 29 June 2013, p. 1] {{Wayback|url=http://eur-lex.europa.eu/LexUriServ/LexUriServ.do?uri=OJ:L:2013:182:0001:0018:EN:PDF |date=20140209191815 }})</ref>

[[斯洛維尼亞人口|斯洛維尼亞公民]]持有[[歐盟護照|歐盟護照]]者也可以[[簽證#签证优惠待遇|免簽證]]的方式入境巴西，停留最多90天。<ref name="visa">[http://www.portalconsular.itamaraty.gov.br/images/qgrv/QGRV-simples-ing-190608.pdf Entry Visas to Brazil] {{Wayback|url=http://www.portalconsular.itamaraty.gov.br/images/qgrv/QGRV-simples-ing-190608.pdf |date=20200731174638 }}, [[Ministry_of_External_Relations_(Brazil)|Ministry of External Relations of Brazil]], August 6, 2019.</ref><ref name="tim">{{Timatic Visa Policy|country=BR|accessdate=1 April 2017}}</ref>

